## Read in data

```{r}
SWEData <- read.csv(file="/Users/amythor86/Desktop/Practice Mapping/SWE_March.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",")
names(SWEData) <- c("Year", "SWE_month", "SWE_mean")
View(SWEData)
library(ggplot2)
str(SWEData)
ggplot(SWEData, aes(x = Year, y = SWE_month)) + geom_point()
```
